    <comment>- update to 0.20.0:
  * docs: Update switcher.json for v0.19.7
  * Add leaflet_method decorator
  * Update README to point to a new plugin
  * Bump actions/setup-python from 4 to 5 in the github-actions
    group
  * Coverage testing
  * Issue 1359
  * **Full Changelog**: https://github.com/python-
    visualization/folium/compare/v0.19.7...v0.20.0
- update to 0.19.7:
  * docs: Update switcher.json for v0.19.6
  * [pre-commit.ci] pre-commit autoupdate
  * Fix or mitigate https://github.com/python-
    visualization/folium/issues…
- update to 0.19.6:
  * Fix numeric keys for dict inputs in tojavascript
  * Docs: explain which layer kinds are base layer / overlay by
    default
  * Docs: update switcher.json for v0.19.5 manually
  * Docs: User guide LayerControl example doesn't work
  * Docs: `utilities.image_to_url()` `'image'` and related
    docstrings
  * Docs: add entry on Search plugin with FeatureGroup
  * Docs: update ImageOverlay with local file example
  * CI: run Geopandas tests
  * Fix Mypy
  * Cleanup MacroElements
  * CI: Run streamlit-folium tests as part of our CI
  * Issue 2125: Fix broken selenium tests</comment>
